interests-body: Joud Nassar, a Software Engineer with a zest for diverse interests, finds joy in coding challenges, exploring emerging technologies, and delving into the world of mobile telecom. Passionate about continuous learning, Joud embraces creativity in problem-solving and innovation.
who-am-i-body: Joud Nassar, a dedicated Software Engineer, holds a degree from Damascus University and contributes significantly to the tech landscape as a Full Stack Developer at Syriatel mobile telecom. Passionate about creating seamless and efficient software solutions, Joud is committed to staying at the forefront of technological advancements. Through expertise acquired at Damascus University and professional experience at Syriatel, Joud stands out as a valuable asset, continually evolving in the dynamic realm of software engineering. With a robust educational foundation, Joud brings a versatile skill set to the field, adept in both front-end and back-end technologies.
